            "description": "One Night Ultimate Alien is similar to other One Night Ultimate... titles in that players each secretly take a role as part of a team, but this time the roles all relate to aliens.\n\nOne Night Ultimate Alien can be combined with any other One Night Ultimate... game.\n\n"
